{"id": 2271, "genre": 1001, "title": "最近三年，你都出于以防万一的目的买过哪些用不着的东西？", "description": "说不准啥时候就要用了，谁知道呢？万一呢？虽然一次也没用过但下回看到害往家买。（题图来自：iStock）", "record_count": 3324, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180409160404tUBoLFfyzWa6Z1Rl.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-04-10T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 274944, "content": "凑单买了蒸脸器~木有卵用~因为懒得用~", "image": "img/option/option/20180410154650HQ6y8Yci41UOCXvm.jpg", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 716017}, {"id": 274946, "content": "结婚时的迎宾纱仪式纱敬酒服秀禾服，穿过一次就在衣柜里挂灰。。。\n各种钢笔彩色墨水漂亮的本子。。。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1302856}, {"id": 274947, "content": "买了把吉他，结果 4 年来摸的时间加起来个小时都没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 846538}, {"id": 283907, "content": "鞋套！资料书！干货！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003171}, {"id": 274948, "content": "怕出门遇上坏人买了便携报警器 但后来出门也懒得带", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285511}, {"id": 274949, "content": "健身卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1309773}, {"id": 275205, "content": "网上淘的衣服，穿了不喜欢又懒得退", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1165019}, {"id": 275717, "content": "买了cd机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1314658}, {"id": 274950, "content": "保险", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269377}, {"id": 275206, "content": "健腹轮", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1307057}, {"id": 277254, "content": "一套带冲击钻的工具箱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274231}, {"id": 274951, "content": "星火英语六级真题试卷", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1307531}, {"id": 275208, "content": "高跟鞋，不磨脚不打脚就是穿着疼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311239}, {"id": 275464, "content": "防狼喷雾", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 581026}, {"id": 274953, "content": "各种高跟鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026473}, {"id": 275466, "content": "2015年3月买了一件衬衫，花花绿绿的\n2018年4月，终于第一次穿了，原因是:搬家把行李打包好了，随便穿一件吧。\n??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1312962}, {"id": 274961, "content": "头发干洗剂?上地铁还差点被拦下来，但是效果令人窒息", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284333}, {"id": 275473, "content": "小西装", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1312978}, {"id": 274962, "content": "推荐书单上的书，买了一大堆", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303735}, {"id": 274964, "content": "怀孕期间双十一屯了1W+的待产用品，一年多了没用完，家里还多了很多废品", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 868692}, {"id": 274967, "content": "英语软件的会员", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294254}, {"id": 275223, "content": "棉质印花灭菌卫生护垫 棉垫 ", "image": "img/option/option/20180411183405xIBUFCRVADjcaMWZ.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108396}, {"id": 275224, "content": "买了香水和口红想送给心仪的人，然而并没有心仪的人可送", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311368}, {"id": 274970, "content": "旅行箱", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1309863}, {"id": 275482, "content": "为了防止僵尸病毒爆发买了一堆砍刀。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1313031}, {"id": 276254, "content": "好看的杯子，盘子，刀叉，想做出米其林水准的摆盘，拍好看的照片", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1318583}, {"id": 275234, "content": "化妆品，买了扔，扔了买", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311478}, {"id": 274979, "content": "看好奇心日报买了滑板和护具，然而只是试了一下，这么大人了不好意思练......", "image": null